<view class="page">
  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="title">AI 议程表</view>
    <view class="muted">管理基础数据、解析接龙并生成可编辑议程。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="title">数据管理</view>
    <view class="muted">当前版本不限制管理权限，所有用户都可以维护基础数据。</view>
    <view class="nav-grid">
      <button class="nav-button" bindtap="openMembersList">会员列表</button>
      <button class="nav-button" bindtap="openPathwaysList">路径列表</button>
      <button class="nav-button" bindtap="openRolesList">角色列表</button>
    </view>
    <button class="wide-button" bindtap="importWorkbook">选择 Excel 导入</button>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="title">议程工具</view>
    <view class="button-row">
      <button type="primary" bindtap="openParseTab">解析议程表</button>
      <button bindtap="openHistory">历史议程</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="status-row">
      <view class="status-label">云环境</view>
      <view class="status-value">{{envId}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
